Ok i had a totally fun weekend like no other! On saturday i went to the electronic music festival and it was fun as all hell. I like that scene, the ravers are now my peoples! after my brother handed me over to my dad we went to sommerset and he let me just wander around and i went to the speedo store where i have a tiny little crush on a guy that works there and i just hung around and talked to himm a bit. After that i got home and relaxed for a bit then went to bed.

      That was Saturday btw. Today i did nothing in the morning except make chocolate-chip pancakes (which were damn good i might add!!). At about 7:00 i went to one of my cousin's wedding where i had a whole lot of fun and hung out with my cuzins and all soo i guess that is all i have to say... Thanks for Listening :)

Today was awesome as all hell. I made $20 babysitting my neices and i had a lot of fun with them while i was doin that, then i went with my older brother Jason and my oldest neice to the movies to see "Holes" which was actually quite good. Then after the movie we went next door to a VERY small fair. After all that excitement we went to Jay's house to see his fiance and his soon to be daughter-in-law, and the pets they have. Finally we drove home and i found out that i am soo wired that i cant sleep. On Saturday me and Jay are goin to DEMPH (is that how its spelled?) in Hart Plaza! I cant wait!! 

C ya :>
